## Bundle Protocol configuration for Node B (Engine 2)
## BPv7 with LTP transport over KISS CLA

## Initialize BP
1

## Add IPN scheme
a scheme ipn 'ipnfw' 'ipnadminep'

## Add local endpoints
a endpoint ipn:2.0 q
a endpoint ipn:2.1 q
a endpoint ipn:2.2 q

## Add LTP protocol
a protocol ltp 1400 100

## Add LTP induct
a induct ltp 2 ltpcli

## Add LTP outduct to Node A (Engine 1)
a outduct ltp 1 ltpclo

## Start BP
s
